A scooter or motor scooter is a motorcycle with step-through frame and a platform for the rider's feet. Elements of scooter design have been present in some of the earliest motorcycles, and motorcycles identifiable as scooters have been made from 1914 or earlier.

[/vc_column_text][vc_btn title="Read More" style="custom" custom_background="#d1bb6e" custom_text="#ffffff" shape="square" size="lg" align="center"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1490101551268{background-image: url(http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/002-retro-bike.jpg?id=3610) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row equal_height="yes" content_placement="middle"][vc_column width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1490100436689{background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" css=".vc_custom_1490102171629{padding-top: 50px !important;padding-right: 50px !important;padding-bottom: 50px !important;padding-left: 50px !important;background-color: #353535 !important;}"][vc_custom_heading text="Retro Scooters" font_container="tag:h2|font_size:50|text_align:center|color:%23ffffff" google_fonts="font_family:Raleway%3A100%2C200%2C300%2Cregular%2C500%2C600%2C700%2C800%2C900|font_style:700%20bold%20regular%3A700%3Anormal"][vc_custom_heading text="Discover Your Lifestyle" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:22|text_align:center|color:%23d1bb6e" google_fonts="font_family:Raleway%3A100%2C200%2C300%2Cregular%2C500%2C600%2C700%2C800%2C900|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]

Scooters are popular for personal transport, partly due to being cheap to buy, easy to operate and convenient to park and store. Most vintage scooters and some newer retro models have an axle-mounted engine.
